description: Reitmans (Canada) Limited primarily engages in the retail sale of women's wear apparel in Canada. It also offers apparel for men. The company serves customers through retail and e-commerce channels. As of April 21, 2022, it operated 404 stores, including 237 Reitmans, 90 Penningtons, and 77 RW&CO. The company was founded in 1926 and is headquartered in Montreal, Canada.
